wpt.desc: More Cowbell? by The GutterBoys, Traditional Cache (2/1.5)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: More Cowbell?
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: Quick little find, with a little bit of history.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
We love the Will Farrell skit on Saturday Night Live where he is playing the cowbell. This actually isn't a cowbell, but the town bell that dates back to 1898. Please read the historical sign next to the cache to learn the history of the bell. Stealth will be required and please BYOP.
Happy Caching!

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Took us just a couple minutes -- and a helpful cachet across the street. :) Found with dawnie22.
